    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ca88f-102"><xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>接口，用于实现 Connection 类，表示与数据源 （例如，网络连接到服务器） 的唯一会话的继承类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca88f-102">The <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interface enables an inheriting class to implement a Connection class, which represents a unique session with a data source (for example, a network connection to a server).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca88f-103">有关连接类的详细信息，请参阅[连接到数据源](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/connecting-to-a-data-source.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca88f-103">For more information about Connection classes, see [Connecting to a Data Source](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/connecting-to-a-data-source.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ca88f-104">应用程序不会创建的实例<xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>接口直接，但创建继承的类的实例<xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca88f-104">An application does not create an instance of the <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interface directly, but creates an instance of a class that inherits <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ca88f-105">继承的类<xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>必须实现所有继承的成员，且通常定义其他成员来添加特定于提供程序的功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca88f-105">Classes that inherit <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> must implement all inherited members, and typically define additional members to add provider-specific functionality.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca88f-106">例如，<xref:System.Data.IDbConnection>接口定义<xref:System.Data.IDbConnection.ConnectionTimeout%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca88f-106">For example, the <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection> interface defines the <xref:System.Data.IDbConnection.ConnectionTimeout%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca88f-107">依次<xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection>类继承此属性，而且还定义了<xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection.PacketSize%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca88f-107">In turn, the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection> class inherits this property, and also defines the <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection.PacketSize%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
